    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"726\" data-end=\"755\">Rite of the Opened Bridge</strong><br data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"758\" /><em data-start=\"758\" data-end=\"780\">Caern Rite • Level 4</em></p><p data-start=\"782\" data-end=\"985\"><strong data-start=\"782\" data-end=\"791\">Time:</strong> 8 hours<br data-start=\"799\" data-end=\"802\" /><strong data-start=\"802\" data-end=\"811\">Cost:</strong> 12 Gnosis from each connected Caern (may be shared by multiple Garou)<br data-start=\"881\" data-end=\"884\" /><strong data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"900\">Requirement:</strong> Two functioning Caerns, each possessing a bound Pathstone or equivalent sacred focus</p><hr data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"990\" /><p data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1261\"><strong data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1007\">Description</strong><br data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1010\" />The Rite of the Opened Bridge forges a Moon Bridge — a permanent spiritual pathway linking two Caerns across vast distance. The bridge exists partially in the Umbra, allowing Garou to travel between sacred sites without crossing the land between them.</p><p data-start=\"1263\" data-end=\"1354\">A Moon Bridge is not convenience magic.<br data-start=\"1302\" data-end=\"1305\" />It is infrastructure born of trust and sacrifice.</p><hr data-start=\"1356\" data-end=\"1359\" /><p data-start=\"1361\" data-end=\"1470\"><strong data-start=\"1361\" data-end=\"1371\">Effect</strong><br data-start=\"1371\" data-end=\"1374\" />When the full Gnosis cost is invested at both Caerns, a <strong data-start=\"1430\" data-end=\"1445\">Moon Bridge</strong> is created between them.</p><p data-start=\"1472\" data-end=\"1501\">While the Moon Bridge exists:</p><ul data-start=\"1502\" data-end=\"1902\"><li data-start=\"1502\" data-end=\"1583\"><p data-start=\"1504\" data-end=\"1583\">Garou may travel between the two Caerns in <strong data-start=\"1547\" data-end=\"1559\">1 minute</strong>, regardless of distance</p></li><li data-start=\"1584\" data-end=\"1658\"><p data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1658\">Entry and exit occur only within the <strong data-start=\"1623\" data-end=\"1644\">area of influence</strong> of each Caern</p></li><li data-start=\"1659\" data-end=\"1707\"><p data-start=\"1661\" data-end=\"1707\">Travel is <strong data-start=\"1671\" data-end=\"1690\">one-way per use</strong>, chosen at entry</p></li><li data-start=\"1708\" data-end=\"1814\"><p data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1814\">Non-Garou may not use the Moon Bridge unless permitted by the Caern’s spirits (Storyteller adjudication)</p></li><li data-start=\"1815\" data-end=\"1902\"><p data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1902\">The Moon Bridge remains in place indefinitely, provided both Caerns remain functional</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1907\" /><p data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1936\"><strong data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1936\">Interaction with Caerns</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1937\" data-end=\"2194\"><li data-start=\"1937\" data-end=\"2011\"><p data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"2011\">The Moon Bridge requires no additional upkeep beyond normal Caern upkeep</p></li><li data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2105\"><p data-start=\"2014\" data-end=\"2105\">If either Caern is lost, or reaches <strong data-start=\"2050\" data-end=\"2066\">Corruption 5</strong>, the Moon Bridge collapses immediately</p></li><li data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2194\"><p data-start=\"2108\" data-end=\"2194\">At <strong data-start=\"2111\" data-end=\"2137\">Corruption 4 or higher</strong>, travel may be narratively strained but remains possible</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2196\" data-end=\"2199\" /><p data-start=\"2201\" data-end=\"2216\"><strong data-start=\"2201\" data-end=\"2216\">Limitations</strong></p><ul data-start=\"2217\" data-end=\"2363\"><li data-start=\"2217\" data-end=\"2301\"><p data-start=\"2219\" data-end=\"2301\">Moon Bridges cannot be redirected or reassigned without performing this Rite again</p></li><li data-start=\"2302\" data-end=\"2363\"><p data-start=\"2304\" data-end=\"2363\">Moon Bridges cannot be used for forced or hostile transport</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2365\" data-end=\"2368\" /><p data-start=\"2370\" data-end=\"2517\"><strong data-start=\"2370\" data-end=\"2394\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"2394\" data-end=\"2397\" /><code data-start=\"2397\" data-end=\"2517\">[GAROU_RITE] type=caern; id=opened-bridge; level=4; cadence=permanent; requires=two-caerns; infrastructure=moon-bridge</code></p>",
