4\" data-end=\"1658\"><p data-start=\"1586\" data-end=\"1658\">Entry and exit occur only within the <strong data-start=\"1623\" data-end=\"1644\">area of influence</strong> of each Caern</p></li><li data-start=\"1659\" data-end=\"1707\"><p data-start=\"1661\" data-end=\"1707\">Travel is <strong data-start=\"1671\" data-end=\"1690\">one-way per use</strong>, chosen at entry</p></li><li data-start=\"1708\" data-end=\"1814\"><p data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1814\">Non-Garou may not use the Moon Bridge unless permitted by the Caern’s spirits (Storyteller adjudication)</p></li><li data-start=\"1815\" data-end=\"1902\"><p data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1902\">The Moon Bridge remains in place indefinitely, provided both Caerns remain functional</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1907\" /><p data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1936\"><strong data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1936\">Interaction with Caerns</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1937\" data-end=\"2194\"><li data-start=\"1937\" data-end=\"2011\"><p data-start=\"1939\" data-end=\"2011\">The Moon Bridge requires no additional upkeep beyond normal Caern upkeep</p></li><li data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2105\"><p data-start=\"2014\" data-end=\"2105\">If either Caern is lost, or reaches <strong data-start=\"2050\" data-end=\"2066\">Corruption 5</strong>, the Moon Bridge collapses immediately</p></li><li data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2194\"><p data-start=\"2108\" data-end=\"2194\">At <strong data-start=\"2111\" data-end=\"2137\">Corruption 4 or higher</strong>, travel may be narratively strained but remains possible</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2196\" data-end=\"2199\" /><p data-start=\"2201\" data-end=\"2216\"><strong data-start=\"2201\" data-end=\"2216\">Limitations</strong></p><ul data-start=\"2217\" data-end=\"2363\"><li data-start=\"2217\" data-end=\"2301\"><p data-start=\"2219\" data-end=\"2301\">Moon Bridges cannot be redirected or reassigned without performing this Rite again</p></li><li data-start=\"2302\" data-end=\"2363\"><p data-start=\"2304\" data-end=\"2363\">Moon Bridges cannot be used for forced or hostile transport</p></li></ul><hr data-start=\"2365\" data-end=\"2368\" /><p data-start=\"2370\" data-end=\"2517\"><strong data-start=\"2370\" data-end=\"2394\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"2394\" data-end=\"2397\" /><code data-start=\"2397\" data-end=\"2517\">[GAROU_RITE] type=caern; id=opened-bridge; level=4; cadence=permanent; requires=two-caerns; infrastructure=moon-bridge</code></p>"
